<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<tag a="110" b="0" />我向<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />借了東西，<delay20 />
過了很久都還沒還……<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />雖然一直覺得不還不行，<delay20 />
但始終沒有付諸行動，<delay8 />
結果光陰流逝，就錯過了歸還的時機……<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="24" />這下子<delay20 />該怎麼辦呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />要我幫你還嗎？</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我會幫你加油的！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子，<delay20 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />到我家來玩的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="20" />忘了把東西帶走啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />雖然想盡快送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />，<delay20 />
但我實在抽不出時間，<delay20 />
所以到現在還沒送去啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我替你跑一趟吧？</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />希望你能早點找到空檔</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實啊，<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的包裹<delay20 />
寄到我家的郵筒裡了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />我想<gender3 m="他" f="她" />應該非常期待<delay20 />
收到這個包裹，<delay20 />
能請你幫忙送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />嗎？</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好啊</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉，現在沒空</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的嗎！？太感謝你了！<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" />請你幫忙這種事，總覺得有點過意不去<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那這東西就拜託你囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以嗎！？真是幫大忙了！<delay frames="40" />
那麼，<delay20 />這個就拜託你囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
你真是太善良了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那，<delay20 />這包裹就拜託你了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />OK～我會加油的！<delay frames="40" />
晚點我就去鄭重道歉，然後物歸原主！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是不可思議，<delay20 />
和你說幾句話，我就能鼓起勇氣了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟是為了<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
我還是擠出時間親自送去吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
你也相當忙碌呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒辦法了，<delay20 />我再自己想辦法處理吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想拜託你一件事情！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />其實啊，為了感謝<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />
平常總是很照顧我，<delay20 />
我特地準備了禮物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="14" />因為想要給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />一個驚喜，<delay8 />
所以想請你把禮物送過去，<delay20 />
你願意幫這個忙嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好啊！</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">抱歉，現在沒空<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是我這輩子最誠懇的請求，<delay20 />
可以請你幫忙嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實，我和<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />
吵架了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我雖然準備了道歉用的禮物，<delay20 />
想要跟<gender3 m="他" f="她" />和好，<delay20 />
但實在是沒有臉去見<gender3 m="他" f="她" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我也不希望<delay20 />
將你無故牽扯進來<tag a="110" b="0" />但還是要厚著臉皮問你，<delay8 />
能不能幫我把禮物送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />呢？</message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">交給我吧！</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這樣子可能不太好……</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好啦──！<delay20 />
謝謝囉，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="14" />我已經可以想像<delay20 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />開心的樣子了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay20 />這禮物就拜託你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" />不<tag a="110" b="0" />光是這五個字，<delay20 />
完全不足以表達出我有多麼感謝你！<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Thank you！<tag a="110" b="4" />！<10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />那邊<delay20 />
就麻煩你啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我才應該跟你道歉，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="40" />
是我這請求太突然了……<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是把自己的感情<tag a="110" b="0" />
直接了當地傳達給對方吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要展現誠意的話，<delay20 />
果然還是得親自去道歉才行呢……<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />雖然還不知道<delay20 />
自己該用什麼表情去見對方<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我決定鼓起勇氣去道歉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，雖然這樣很像在催促你，<delay20 />
但如果你能在今天內幫忙送過去，
我會很高興的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天已經很晚了，<delay20 />
所以明天再幫我送過去就OK囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />有沒有生氣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你不要忘記把<gender3 m="他" f="她" />借我的東西<delay20 />
送回去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="24" />希望<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />現在<delay20 />
沒有因此感到困擾<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你幫忙把<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />忘記帶走的東西<delay20 />
好好地送到<gender3 m="他" f="她" />手上喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你盡快<delay20 />把那個包裹送過去吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是讓<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />擔心<delay20 />
就不好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
別忘記這是個驚喜！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不動聲色地送出去喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然拜託你幫這種忙讓我很過意不去，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但還是麻煩你幫我把道歉的禮物<tag a="110" b="0" />
送給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>